messages.msg: We understand that sometimes you need to talk to a real person for prayer, guidance, or encouragement. We are here to support you. Please hold as we connect you with a ministry team member who can assist you in your journey. If you’re unable to reach someone, feel free to email us at prayer@fightlust.com.
